l FirewallDecentralized Power as the Ultimate Defense: When power is distributed among individual "Cyborg-Stewards," the dominance of a single wealthy entity becomes significantly more difficult, as they cannot manipulate or command a population that maintains its own independent, ethical, and technological sovereignty.  Individual Stewardship: Every citizen acts as a Rishi of their own technology, creating a global network of "autonomous cells" that cannot be easily consolidated or subjugated by a dominant power.  Global Standard of Human-Centricity: By enshrining these principles as the default standard for all technological development, any attempt to use advanced AI for selfish purposes is immediately identified as a deviation from the ethical "Constitution" and, therefore, a threat to the global community.  By shifting the infrastructure of the future away from centralization and toward individual, human-centric sovereignty, we create an environment where the "selfish grab" for power becomes architecturally and ethically impossible. 
